==發行==
2015年2月25日，[[STX娛樂|STX娛樂]]將美國上映日定為2016年3月11日<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lang|first1=Brent|title=STX Entertainment Dates Films With Matthew McConaughey, Julia Roberts, Jason Blum|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/stx-entertainment-dates-films-with-matthew-mcconaughey-julia-roberts-jason-blum-1201441515/|accessdate=2015-03-06|publisher=variety.com|date=2015-02-25|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612135908/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/stx-entertainment-dates-films-with-matthew-mcconaughey-julia-roberts-jason-blum-1201441515/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年10月，STX娛樂將日期延期至2016年5月13日<ref>{{cite news|last1=Busch|first1=Anita|title=STX Pushes ‘Free State Of Jones’ To Summer 2016, Dates ‘The Space Between Us’|url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/the-free-state-of-jones-release-date-matthew-mcconaughey-the-space-between-us-1201591487/|accessdate=2015-10-28|work=deadline.com|date=2015-10-22|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612163416/https://deadline.com/2015/10/the-free-state-of-jones-release-date-matthew-mcconaughey-the-space-between-us-1201591487/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年3月，電影又被改至2016年6月24日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=McClintock|first1=Pamela|title=Matthew McConaughey's 'Free State of Jones' Goes Up Against 'Independence Day: Resurgence'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/matthew-mcconaugheys-free-state-jones-874074|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2015-03-09|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212024957/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/matthew-mcconaugheys-free-state-jones-874074|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

首支預告片於2016年1月9日釋出<ref>Ryan Parker, [http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/matthew-mcconaughey-starrer-free-state-853673 "Matthew McConaughey Starrer 'Free State of Jones' Trailer Released,"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/matthew-mcconaughey-starrer-free-state-853673 |date=20201126161728 }} ''The Hollywood Reporter'', January 9, 2016 In front of The Revenant..</ref>。

==反響==
電影獲得了兩極的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度40%，該網站共識：「《烈火邊境》有著崇高的目標，但它們的呆板待遇都不足以彌補其迷人的史實」<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/free_state_of_jones/ |title=Free State of Jones (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116053133/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/free_state_of_jones |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分54<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/free-state-of-jones |title=Free State of Jones reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108110041/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/free-state-of-jones |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在美國和加拿大，電影於2016年6月24日與《[[ID4星際重生|ID4星際重生]]》、《[[絕鯊島|絕鯊島]]》共同上映競爭，預計首映週末能從2815間戲院獲得1200萬美元左右的票房<ref name=budget/>。美國首映週末票房為780萬美元位居當週第五<ref name="opening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/independence-day-resurgence-finding-dory-shallows-free-state-of-jones-neon-demon-weekend-box-office-1201778773/|title=‘Dory’ Posts Record Second Weekend For Animated Movie As Fireworks Die For ‘Resurgence’; ‘Shallows’ Chomps $16M+|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2016-06-26|accessdate=2016-06-26|archive-date=2016-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160626234146/http://deadline.com/2016/06/independence-day-resurgence-finding-dory-shallows-free-state-of-jones-neon-demon-weekend-box-office-1201778773/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

